.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: july, august, may, december, november
There are 5 different nationalities: english, spanish, ukranian, norwegian, japanese
5 different games are played: chess, go, scrabble, whist, poker
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea, milk, orange-juice, water
City: venice, berlin, miami, hannover, nizza

1. the english is the person who's birthday is in july
2. the spanish is the person traveling to venice
3. the person drinking coffee is the person who's birthday is in august
4. the ukranian is the person drinking tea
5. the person who's birthday is in august is to the right of the person who's birthday is in may
6. the person playing chess is the person traveling to nizza
7. the person playing go is the person who's birthday is in december
8. the person drinking milk is in the middle
9. the norwegian is on the far left
10. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the person traveling to berlin
11. the person playing go is to the left or right of the person traveling to hannover
12. the person playing whist is the person drinking orange-juice
13. the japanese is the person playing poker
14. the norwegian is to the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Nationality	|   norwegian	|    ukranian	|     english	|    spanish	|    japanese	|
| Birthday		|    december	|      november	|      july	|     may	|     august	|
| Beverage	|     water	|      tea	|      milk	| orange-juice	|     coffee	|
| Game		|     go	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| whist	|   parliament	|
| City		|     berlin	|     hannover	|     nizza	|     venice	|     miami	|
